<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Redirecting…</title>
  <script>
    // Central map of slugs -> targets
    const MAP = {
      instalacion: "https://youtu.be/oHNBdp1jUzY",
      cartaporte: "https://youtu.be/k1EAHYGkRfI",
      manifiesto: "https://youtu.be/R2y7PsGtiXE"
    };

    (function () {
      const slug = (location.hash || "").replace(/^#/, "").trim();
      const target = MAP[slug];
      if (target) {
        location.replace(target);   // no history entry
      } else {
        // fallback (optional): send to a hub page
        location.replace("/videos/");
      }
    })();
  </script>
</head>
<body>Redirecting…</body>
</html>
